import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { MatDialog } from '@angular/material/dialog'; import { ModalGoSessionComponent } from './components/modal-go-session/modal-go-session.component'; import { ModalTypeSessionComponent } from './components/modal-type-session/modal-type-session.component'; import { ModalSequenceService } from './services/modal-sequence.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-sessions', templateUrl: './sessions.component.html', styleUrls: ['./sessions.component.scss'], }) export class SessionsComponent { iconAdd = 'assets/images/icons/add.svg'; iconUser = 'assets/images/icons/user.svg'; constructor( public dialog: MatDialog, private modalSequence: ModalSequenceService ) {} startSession() { this.modalSequence.goSession(); } }
Olá, Fernanda!
Vamos organizar suas sessões diárias.
Arraste e solte um paciente aqui
ou use o botão “Iniciar Sessão”.
